' Model: Claude Opus 4.8 (1M context)
' Created: 2026-07-04
' Pluggable technique (b) — delegate object (GoF p.143).
' Models java/dev/kaldiroglu/adapter/gof/pluggable/electricity/delegate/.

@startuml pluggable-b-delegate
title Technique (b) — Delegate Object (pluggable via composition)

skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam shadowing false
hide empty members

interface TurkishPowerSource <<Target>> {
  +turnOn()
  +turnOff()
}

interface PowerDelivery <<narrow interface>> {
  +deliver()
  +cut()
}

class DelegatingPowerAdapter <<Adapter>> {
  -delivery : PowerDelivery
  +turnOn()
  +turnOff()
}

class USPowerDelivery <<delegate>> {
  -us : USPowerSource
  +deliver()
  +cut()
}

class UKPowerDelivery <<delegate>> {
  -uk : UKPowerSource
  +deliver()
  +cut()
}

class USPowerSource <<Adaptee>> {
  +pushSwitch()
}

class UKPowerSource <<Adaptee>> {
  +flipToggle()
}

TurkishPowerSource <|.. DelegatingPowerAdapter
DelegatingPowerAdapter o--> PowerDelivery : forwards to
PowerDelivery <|.. USPowerDelivery
PowerDelivery <|.. UKPowerDelivery
USPowerDelivery --> USPowerSource
UKPowerDelivery --> UKPowerSource

note right of DelegatingPowerAdapter
  On adapter class; swap the delegate
  to re-target. No subclassing.
end note
@enduml
